N. G. Wade, et al., Plaintiffs in Error, v. The Fidelity Mutual Life Insurance Company, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Duval. H. L. Anderson and Odom, Crawford & Butler, for Plaintiffs in Error; E. J. L’Engle and W. E. Balcer, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for defendant in error.
